# It seems there was no output from the last command, which may indicate that the movement to the nearest coal resource was successful but did not yield any additional information.

# I will now attempt to harvest coal from the nearest coal resource to ensure I have enough for smelting iron ore. 
# I will aim to gather at least 10 units of coal to facilitate the smelting process.

harvest_resource(nearest(Resource.Coal), quantity=10)  # Harvest 10 units of coal from the nearest coal resource. 
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Check the inventory after harvesting coal. 
print(f"Entities on the map: {get_entities()}")  # Check the updated state of entities.
